HEADWORD: Wistit
<hw>Wis"tit</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. from native name: cf. F.
<ets>ouistiti</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small South
American monkey; a marmoset.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>wistiti</asp>, and <asp>ouistiti</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
